{
  "texts": [
    "That said, PR-targeted methods offer advantages in, e.g., better generalisability and clean accuracy.",
    "The very recent \"hybrid\" training method combines the advantages of both, but at the price of training efficiency.",
    "Key contributions of this paper include:",
    "• Benchmarking: After formalizing a general formulation of the PR-targeted training methods, we develop the first benchmark dedicated for PR, evaluating a broad set of training methods with metrics of AR, PR, accuracy, generalisability, and efficiency.",
    "• Analysis: Analysis is provided based on both empirical and theoretical studies, highlighting the strengths, limitations, and trade-offs among training methods in the context of improving PR."
  ]
}